ECB’s Costa Says Lehman Collapse Still Having Repercussions

-- B y   H e n r i q u e   A l m e i d a
-- 
2011-09-19T09:21:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/ecb-s-costa-says-lehman-collapse-still-having-repercussions.html
European Central Bank Governing
Council Member Carlos Costa said “we are still suffering”
repercussions from the collapse of  Lehman Brothers .  Costa, who also heads the Bank of  Portugal , spoke today at
a conference in Lisbon.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Henrique Almeida in Lisbon at 
